											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Minsc transfers Boo to his shoulder and strikes a pose, declaiming heroically - then breaks down giggling when Boo crawls inside his armour. &#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Puts the Hamster on his right shoulder (collar bone level) with his left hand, let Boo crawl on his shoulder and in his armour and strikes a pose, then laugh" />
